:#  Module	    Exec                                                      #
:#                                                                            #
:#  Description     Run a command, logging its output to the log file.        #
:#                                                                            #
:#                  In VERBOSE mode, display the command line first.          #
:#                  In DEBUG mode, display the command line and the exit code.#
